commit.message:
[VP] Fix 4K monitor failed to run videowall 4k on multi channel

Enlarge max patched/kernel/csc matrix number to fix 4k multi channel issue.

[Encode] add nullptr check for hwInterface

add nullptr check for hwInterface.

[Media Common] [VP] MCPY linear surface dump rework and minor fixes

Current media copy surface dump is not working because of infinite recursive calling. Rework linear surface dump and abandon tile surface dump.
Also make some minor fixes.

SR new model for perf tuning: cache issue

Enable Lace cache table for tuning cache
